    "[32]The scheme contains a semi-trusted party which is vulnerable to attacks.",
    "Cluster Computing (2024) 27:7981-8000 7985 PoW is the consensus mechanism originally used within blockchain technology.",
    "All transactions made on the blockchain are recorded in an open ledger.",
    "Transactions are verified and executed with the consent of the majority of users in the network, rather than a third-party.",
    "This operation is called PoW."
